Dear Team,

Following the recent DST transition, we identified an opportunity to further strengthen time synchronization consistency on UK devices.

As part of a continuous improvement initiative, we have implemented an Intune proactive remediation automation that periodically validates and maintains correct time configuration. The automation:
- Ensures devices are set to GMT Standard Time (UK with DST support)
- Confirms automatic DST adjustment is enabled
- Verifies the Windows Time service is running and triggers a resynchronization if required

This runs silently in the background and prevents the need for manual device-level interventions during future DST changes.

- User impact: None  
- Risk level: Low  
- Rollback: Automation can be disabled if required  

Please let us know if any further details are needed.

Kind regards,  
Mohit Srivastava  
Intune Operations  

